---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Window Replacement City of Casey | Full Service Area | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Window and sliding-door replacement contractors across the full City of Casey — Berwick, Cranbourne, Narre Warren, Hampton Park, Endeavour Hills, Clyde North, Officer. AS 2047 compliant, double-glazing, free measure & quote."
  canonical="https://berwickwindowreplacement.com.au/city-of-casey/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">City of Casey &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>Window replacement across the <span class="accent">City of Casey</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From Endeavour Hills in the north-west across to Clyde North and
        Officer in the south-east. Older 70s&ndash;80s estates with end-of-life
        aluminium and steel-frame windows, 90s&ndash;2000s brick-veneer stock
        with chalky single-glaze frames, and brand-new estates upgrading to
        bigger sliders and bifolds &mdash; we cover the lot.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free measure</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>Per-suburb guides &mdash; typical housing age, common window stock, what we usually spec.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/berwick/">Berwick</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/cranbourne/">Cranbourne</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/narre-warren/">Narre Warren</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/hampton-park/">Hampton Park</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/endeavour-hills/">Endeavour Hills</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other City of Casey suburbs we cover.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Beaconsfield</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Berwick East</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Berwick Springs</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Edenrise</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Clyde</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Clyde North</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cranbourne East</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cranbourne North</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cranbourne West</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cranbourne South</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Doveton</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lynbrook</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lyndhurst</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lysterfield South</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Narre Warren South</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Narre Warren North</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Officer</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Three eras, three window conversations.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>1970s&ndash;80s stock</strong> (Endeavour Hills, Hampton Park,
          older Cranbourne, Doveton): steel-frame casements and first-gen
          aluminium, both at end of working life. Full frame replacement,
          aluminium swap-in, double-glaze upgrade highly recommended for
          comfort and condensation.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>1990s&ndash;2000s stock</strong> (Berwick Springs, Narre Warren,
          Cranbourne West, most of Hampton Park infill): builder-spec single-glaze
          aluminium hitting its 25&ndash;35 year mark. Powder coat chalky,
          rubber seals failed, sliders worn. Full re-window jobs &mdash;
          12&ndash;15 windows over 2&ndash;4 days &mdash; the standard
          City of Casey job.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>2010s&ndash;current stock</strong> (Edenrise, Clyde North,
          Cranbourne East, Officer, Berwick Waters): builder-spec windows
          are fine. Owners call us for upsizing &mdash; 2.4m rear sliders
          to 3.6m or 4.2m stackers, bifolds, additional kitchen-side
          awnings for cross-ventilation.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">AS 2047 and energy compliance.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>AS 2047:</strong> Australian Standard for residential windows &mdash; wind load, water tightness, glass safety, operating force. Every window we install is stamped compliant.</li>
          <li><strong>NCC 2022 / 2025 energy provisions:</strong> apply to new builds and major alterations. Like-for-like replacement in an existing house generally doesn&rsquo;t trigger a new energy report.</li>
          <li><strong>WERS energy ratings:</strong> U-value and SHGC labels on the windows you choose &mdash; we provide these for any job that needs them.</li>
          <li><strong>Glass safety (AS 1288):</strong> windows below 500mm above floor level, near doors, or in wet areas must be Grade A safety glass &mdash; standard inclusion on all our work.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five formats</span>
      <h2>What we install.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/aluminium-windows/"><h3>Aluminium windows</h3><p>$400&ndash;$1,200/window. Sliding, awning, double-hung, fixed. The Casey default.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/timber-windows/"><h3>Timber windows</h3><p>$800&ndash;$2,400/window. Sash and casement, heritage match or premium new build.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/sliding-doors/"><h3>Sliding doors</h3><p>$2.5K&ndash;$8K. Standard 2-panel up to 6m stacker openings.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/bifold-doors/"><h3>Bifold doors</h3><p>$5K&ndash;$12K. Concertina-fold 3 to 5 panels, true indoor-outdoor flow.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/awning-windows/"><h3>Awning windows</h3><p>$450&ndash;$900/window. Kitchen, bathroom, laundry &mdash; rain-protected ventilation.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free measure-up anywhere in the City of Casey.</h2>
        <p>Old-estate full re-window or new-build slider upgrade. Fixed quote in 7 days.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
